    <p>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci provides professional <strong>DCS appliance repair</strong> for homeowners with premium outdoor cooking, refrigeration, beverage, ice, heating, and outdoor kitchen appliances. We service <strong>DCS outdoor grills, Series 9 grills, Series 7 grills, built-in grills, freestanding grills, side burners, power burners, griddles, outdoor refrigerators, beer dispensers, ice makers, beverage chillers, patio heaters, grill carts, storage drawers, and outdoor kitchen systems</strong> with careful diagnostics, detail-focused workmanship, and respect for the appliance’s design, finish, and installation.</p>

